{
  "stem": "13874.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And being naturally inclined, I wound up taking-- in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had a little hospital there-- being a helper.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mostly colds, maybe a few injuries.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Serious ones were shipped to the local hospital in Ramsgate.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were two Englishmen, and the rest were, I think, [INAUDIBLE] from Germany.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Refugees.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Refugees.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were allowed to leave within five miles of the camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I also had a bike I bought.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I could go to Ramsgate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was summer.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I could go to the beach or go to Richborough, Sandwich, which was a close by town.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was permissible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that five-mile limit was flexible.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were there-- I was there less than two months when the war in Europe broke out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And pretty soon afterwards, the British liked to-- would like to get the camp back.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] started out first recruiting some of us for the Pioneer Corps, which was a fancy name for a labor battalion.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were actually able to form out of-- from the refugees to [INAUDIBLE], which in the beginning were part of the camp in one section.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But later on, just after I left, they deported all non-military and interred some on the Isle of Man.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they went from one internment camp to another.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the British considered us Germans and treated us accordingly.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They hated Jews to start out with, and they were not very fond of refugees.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I could tell stories, mostly hearsay, some personal, about how the British react to the German refugees in England.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It's not very salutary.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I don't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Actually, nothing happened to me, personally, but-- because I left.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
